kāravaṇamāhātmyam|
śrīgaṇeśāya namaḥ| śrīlakuṭapāṇaye namaḥ|
amaragaṇaniṣevyaḥ sarvasiddhapradātā
kaliyugam avatīrṇaḥ kāyarūpī maheśaḥ|
sakalabhuvanakartā sarvapāpaprahatā
diśatu lakuṭapāṇirvo vibhūtiṃ prasannaḥ|| 1 ||

kailāsaśikharārūḍhaṃ bhagavantaṃ trilocanam|
mahādevaṃ mahākālaṃ mahābhairavarūpiṇam|| 2 ||

ekākinaṃ prabhuṃ dṛṣṭvā papraccha pārvatī tadā|

śrīdevyuvāca |

paṭṭabandhasya māhātmyaṃ vistarāt kathaya prabho|| 3 ||

īśvara uvāca |

kalidvāparayormadhye avatāraṃ mama śṛṇu|
yasya smaraṇamātreṇa mucyate sarvapātakaiḥ|| 4 ||

atrināmā tu devaṛṣiḥ pūrvaṃ khyāto mahātapāḥ|
tadanvaye prasūto 'asau viśvarūpo mahādvijaḥ|| 5 ||

sudarśanastu deveśi tasya patnī sudarśanā|
sarvalakṣaṇasampannā rūpalāvaṇyasaṃyutā|| 6 ||

harṣagadgadasambhāṣā mattamātaṅgagāminī|
sampūrṇendumukhī subhrūḥ kuraṅgacakitekṣaṇā|
pativratadharā sādhvī patyurādeśakāriṇī|| 7 ||

yathā rūpaṃ tathā śīlaṃ sādhvīnāṃ dhurī kīrtitā|
brahmarātryavasāne tu prathame ca caturyuge|| 8 ||

avatīrṇo hyaham martye ulkāgrāme vilomataḥ|
vīrabhadro gaṇo nāma [...] [...] tasya varānane|| 9 ||

tasya caikāgrato bhakteravatīrṇaḥ svayam tataḥ|
upapannastato garbhe māsi bhādrapade tadā|| 10 ||

devakāryasya kāryārthaṃ martyaloke varānane|
evaṃ caivāśvino māsastathā vai kārttiko gataḥ|| 11 ||

atha mārgaśiro māsastathā pauṣaḥ prakīrtitaḥ|
māghamāso gato devi tathā vai phālgunaḥ smṛtaḥ|| 12 ||

samprāpte caitramāse tu śuklapakṣe caturdaśī|
ardharātre vyatīte tu prasūtā sā kulāṅganā|| 13 ||

sūtikāsthā mahādevi mahāsatyavatī satī|
apaśyadātmano bālaṃ jātamātraṃ varānane|| 14 ||

piṅgākṣaṃ piṅgakeśaṃ ca taptakāñcanasaṃnibham|
sudṛḍhaṃ bāhuyugalaṃ ūrū ca suḍrḍhau tathā|| 15 ||

parasparaṃ vadantyevaṃ paśya bālaṃ guṇānvitam|
viśvarūpo mahāprājñastāsāṃ vākyena sundari|| 16 ||

āmantrayat tato viprān vedavedāṅgapāragān|
akrūrān satyasambhāṣān sarvabhūtahite ratān|| 17 ||

etadguṇasamāyuktān kṛtsnān āmantrya bhaktitaḥ|
śucirbhūtvā mahādevi jātakarma cakāra saḥ|| 18 ||

yājñavalkyavasiṣṭhābhyāṃ tathā pārāśareṇa ca|
vedoktenaiva kāryeṇa vidhiṃ kūryāt prayatnataḥ|| 19 ||

tapayāmāsa tān viprān dānaiśca vividhaiḥ śubhaiḥ|
hiraṇyaṃ rajataṃ vastraṃ gāvo dhānyaṃ ca medinī|| 20 ||

evaṃ vidhopacāraiśca pūjitā vividhā dvijāḥ|
dadhyakṣatakuśairdūrvā[...] [...] kaiśca varānane|| 21 ||

yajet prajāpatiṃ vidhyā vedānāṃ smaraṇaṃ tathā|
āśīrvādaṃ dadurviprā jīvatputro bhava dvija|| 22 ||

tataḥ putramukhaṃ dṛṣṭvā vedaghoṣeṇa pārvati|
evaṃ caitro 'atha vaiśākhastathā jyeṣṭho varānane|| 23 ||

āṣāḍhaḥ śrāvaṇānte ca grahaṇaṃ bhāskarasya ca|
tataḥ śrutvā brāhmaṇebhya idam vacanam abravīt|| 24 ||

sukhāsīnau mahādevi dampatī śayanaṃ gatau|
parasparaṃ vadantyevam ālāpairmadhurasvaraiḥ|| 25 ||

śrūyate ca purāṇebhya idaṃ proktaṃ varānane|
tasmiṃstīrthe kurukṣetre sarvakāmārthasādhane|| 26 ||

yo dadāti viśālākṣi yathāśaktyā tu kāñcanam|
kanyāśca rajataṃ vastraṃ gāvo dhānyaṃ ca medinīm|| 27 ||

akṣayyaṃ tu bhavet tasya rāhugraste divākare|
viṣṇunā varadānena tatrākṣayyaṃ prakīrttitam|| 28 ||

tena santaḥ praśaṃsanti kurukṣetraṃ tataḥ param|
yadā tatraiva gantavyaṃ grahaṇe bhāskarasya tu|| 29 ||

uddhareccāgnihotraṃ ca yāvannodayate raviḥ|
astaṃ gate divānāthe homaṃ dadyādyathāvidhi|| 30 ||

vaiśvadevaṃ ca madhyāhne pañcayajñaṃ ca kārayet|
āgate svāgataṃ kuryādāsanaṃ ca pradāpayet|| 31 ||

bhaktipūrvopadiṣṭena yathāśaktyā tu bhojanam|
śrībālavṛddheṣvaśanaṃ vāsaṃ vātiprayatnataḥ|| 32 ||

svāgataṃ na dadātyevaṃ gṛhasthaḥ patito bhavet|
pratiśrayastu sarvebhyo dātavyo gṛhamedhinā|| 33 ||

yatiśca brahmacārī ca pakvānnasvāmināvubhau|
teṣāṃ bhakṣā pradātavyā yatīnāṃ tu susaṃskṛtā|| 34 ||

sukṛtaṃ yat kṛtaṃ kiṃcidājanma maraṇāntakam|
anyathā hanti tat sarvaṃ gṛhasthairnārcito yadi|| 35 ||

pūjite pūjitāḥ sarve manuṣyāḥ pitṛdevatāḥ|
tasmāt sarvaprayatnena so 'atithisargasaṃkramaḥ|| 36 ||

kāle prāptastvakāle vā pathiko 'atibubhukṣitaḥ|
pūjito vividhān bhogān saṃdadyānnātra saṃśayaḥ|| 37 ||

āyuḥ prajāśca vittaṃ ca dadāti pūjito 'atithiḥ|
kupito harate sarvaṃ puṇyaṃ bṛhaspaterapi|| 38 ||

etat sarvaṃ viśeṣeṇa yathoddiṣṭaṃ tu pālayet|
pativratā tu yā nārī pativākyānuyāyinī|| 39 ||

sā vandyā triṣu lokeṣu iti śāstrasya niścayaḥ|
mātāpitrośca yā bhaktyā saṃyutā vratacāriṇī|| 40 ||

praviśya hṛdayaṃ nityaṃ devairapi hi pūjyate|
evaṃ vākyāvasāne tu bālaṃ yatnena rakṣaya|| 41 ||

kumāraiḥ saha vartantaṃ ramamānaṃ mudā pathi|
tvayā bālo viśālākṣi rakṣitavyaḥ prayatnataḥ|| 42 ||

utsaṅge sā tataḥ kṛtvā bālaṃ paśyati sā priyā|
cakṣurbhyām aśrapūrṇābhyāṃ mukham ālokayat tadā|| 43 ||

svajanā bāndhavā ye ca śyālāḥ sambandhinastadā|
vidyārthinastu ye viprā ye cānye āśritā janāḥ|| 44 ||

kṛtāñjaliḥ puro bhūtvā bālaṃ yatnena rakṣata|
evaṃ samarpayan bālaṃ kurukṣetraṃ pratasthivān|| 45 ||

iti śrīvāyupūrāṇaḥ śivaprasūtisargaḥ||

ataḥ paraṃ pravakṣyāmi kumāracaritaṃ param|
yanna kasyacidākhyātaṃ tat sarvaṃ kathayāmi te|| 1 ||

pativratā tu sā nārī putrayuktā dhanānvitā|
bhartṛvākyānuvartantī yathoddiṣṭena karmaṇā|| 2 ||

uṣaḥkāle tu samprāpte śucirbhūtvā tu sā priyā|
saṃmārjya homaśālāyāṃ gomayenānulepayat|| 3 ||

samidhaḥ sruvaṃ srucaṃ caiva akṣatāṃśca tathā ghṛtam|
tathā darbhān mahādevi kṛtvā ca dharaṇītale|| 4 ||

abhyukṣaṇaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā gatā bāhye śubhānanā|
homaṃ dadati te sarve bālāḥ sambandhinastathā|| 5 ||

dine dine tu sā devi yathoddiṣṭaṃ cakāra ha|
tathā cāśvayuje māsi samprāpte ca śubhānane|| 6 ||

tato 'anyasmin dine devi pūrvāhṇe śubhakarmaṇā|
āsādya tu sruvaṃ darbhān saghṛtaṃ tāmrabhājanam|| 7 ||

abhyukṣaṇaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā gatā bāhye tu sundari|
brāhmaṇaṃ ca tato gṛhya gṛhaṃ prāptā tapasvinī|| 8 ||

gatāgnihotraśālāyāṃ susamiddhaṃ hutāśanam|
agnihotrasya tat kāryaṃ homadravyasya niṣkṛtim|| 9 ||

paśyamānā viśālākṣī vismayāviṣṭacetasā|
jaharṣa ca tataḥ kṛtvā citte buddhiḥ prayojitā|| 10 ||

brāhmaṇastadanujñāto homaṃ dattaṃ cintayan|
gataḥ svamandiram āścaryaṃ paśyantī sā dine dine|| 11 ||

cintayantī paraṃ guhyaṃ rahasyaṃ kautukaṃ param|
bālarūpādhikaṃ jñātvā sā cintāvaśamāgatā|| 12 ||

tyaktanidrā tu sā devi iti cintya muhurmuhuḥ|
īdṛśaṃ katham āścaryaṃ kasya nākhyāpayāmyaham|| 13 ||

homaṃ dadati pitaro mama kāruṇyabuddhayaḥ|
kiṃ devā ṛṣayaḥ siddhā viśvedevāstrayo 'agnayaḥ|| 14 ||

homaṃ dattvā kathaṃ yānti kṣaṇamātreṇa sarvadā|
āścaryaṃ paramaṃ guhyaṃ paśyāmi tu dine dine|| 15 ||

evaṃ sā cintayitvā tu tato nidrāvaśamāgatā|
prabhāte putrakaṃ devi aṅke kṛtvā tapasvinī|| 16 ||

panthānam īkṣate nārī udvignamanasā priye|
sā pṛcchati pathi kṣīṇān rūkṣakeśāṃśca dhūsarān|| 17 ||

saputraiḥ sakalatraiśca bhrātṛbhiḥ svajanaistathā|
dagdhā viyogaduḥkhena kṛṣṇadehābhavat tadā|| 18 ||

kāṅkṣamāṇā divārātrau snehāt tu darśanaṃ pateḥ|
cintayantī tadā devi nityam udvignacetasā|| 19 ||

kurukṣetragatān devi pathi kṣīṇān samāgatān|
saṃghātavartino dṛṣṭvā duḥkhitā sā pativratā|| 20 ||

aśrupūrṇā sunetrā ca citrāṅgī madhurasvarā|
gṛhe prāptā tu sā devi kāṅkṣantī bharturāgamam|| 21 ||

aparāhṇe mahābhāge āgato munisattamaḥ|
snātvā cāsau kurukṣetre puṇyatīrthe śubhānane|| 22 ||

āsanaṃ ca tadā devi tathā vistīrṇam ādarāt|
pādaśaucaṃ mahādevi kṛtaṃ viprasya yatnataḥ|| 23 ||

dadhyakṣataṃ tathā dūrvā sitatoyaṃ suśobhanam|
nikṣipya ca śubhe pātre tato 'avardhāpayat patim|| 24 ||

bāndhavāḥ svajanāḥ sarve saṃgine āśritā janāḥ|
kurukṣetrāgataṃ jñātvā āgatā myā(?)gatapriyāḥ|| 25 ||

taiḥ sambhāṣya yathānyāyaṃ hṛṣṭacitto 'abhavaddvijaḥ|
iṣṭabhojyaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā homaṃ dattvā varānane|| 26 ||

pathi śrānto mahādevi brāhmaṇaḥ śayanaṃ gataḥ|
gṛhakāryaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā saṃsupte sakāle jane|| 27 ||

śayyānte copaviṣṭā ca priyā vacanam abravīt|
kuśalenāgatastīrthe puṇyakṣetre mahāmune|| 28 ||

dattvā dānaṃ supātre ca kṣemeṇāgato gṛham|

brāhmaṇa uvāca |

śṛṇu bhadre pravakṣyāmi gatastīrthe yathā priye|
avighnena ca samprāptastava snehena sundari|| 29 ||

durlabhaṃ priyam ākhyeyaṃ durlabhaṃ jīvitaṃ dhanam|
durlabhā tvādṛśī bhāryā durlabho guṇavān sutaḥ|| 30 ||

durlabhā jananī loke pitā caiva viśeṣitaḥ|
durlabhaṃ sādhusanmānaṃ durlabhaṃ tīrthasevanam|| 31 ||

smarāmi te divārātrau caritaṃ śobhanaṃ priye|
na smarāmi viśālākṣi kadācit tava vipriyam|| 32 ||

bhāryā nāma nṛṇāṃ bhadre sarvakāmārthasādhinī|
yaśaḥ śriyaḥ kāmayuktā putradā kulavardhinī|
bhāryāhīno viśālākṣi kuto bhadrāṇi paśyati|| 33 ||

kuśalaṃ tava bālasya kuśalaṃ tava sundari|
kuśalaṃ dhanadhānye ca kuśalaṃ svajane jane|| 34 ||

agnihotraṃ ca sātithyaṃ pādaśaucaṃ pratiśrayaḥ|
aśeṣaṃ sarvam ityetat tvayā yatnena pālitam|| 35 ||

sudarśanā uvāca |

sātithyam agnihotraṃ ca pādaśaucaṃ pratiśrayaḥ|
yathā sarvam anujñātaṃ tat tathā sudṛḍhaṃ kṛtam|| 36 ||

viśvarūpa uvāca |

sādhu sādhu mahābhāge priye sarvāṅgasundari|
pativrate viśālākṣi ratiputrapravardhini|| 37 ||

vividhāni ca duḥkhāni anyajanmakṛtāni ca|
tvaddarśanena naśyanti raviṃ dṛṣṭvā yathā himam|| 38 ||

sudarśanā uvāca |

abhayaṃ dehi me kānta rahasyaṃ kathayāmi te|
akathyaṃ sarvalokānāṃ yanna vṛttaṃ kathaṃcana|| 39 ||

viśvarūpa uvāca |

akathyaṃ paramaṃ guhyaṃ yat tvayā kautukaṃ param|
dṛṣṭaṃ kathaya me 'aśeṣaṃ mayi snehena sundari|| 40 ||

śrīsudarśanā uvāca |

yat tvayā samanujñātam agnihotrasya pālanam|
tat tathā kriyamāṇasya ahanyahani suvratam|| 41 ||

apare ca dine homadravyaṃ śruvaṃ śrucaṃ tathā|
abhyukṣaṇaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā saghṛtaṃ tāmrabhājanam|| 42 ||

aśeṣaṃ sthāpayitvā tu durbhān samidha eva ca|
bāhye gatvātivegena punarāgamanaṃ kṛtam|| 43 ||

hutadravyaṃ ca paśyāmi vidhiyuktaṃ dine dine|
etanme kautukaṃ kānta rahasyaṃ kathitaṃ tava|| 44 ||

viśvarūpa uvāca |

pracchanaṃ tu nirīkṣāmi sandhyāyāṃ virate ravau|
yena me saṃśayo bhadre na kadācit pravartate|| 45 ||

īśvara uvāca |

ardharātre vyatīte tu dampatī śayanaṃ gatau|
tataḥ prabhātasamaye homaṃ dattvā yathāvidhi|| 46 ||

madhyāhne vaiśvadevaṃ tu kṛtam ātithyabhojanam|
aparāhṇe tu samprāpte kṛtvā saṃmārjanaṃ priye|| 47 ||

abhyukṣaṇaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā homadravyaṃ susaṃskṛtam|
sandhyākāle tu samprāpte 'agniruddhṛtya saṃskṛtaḥ|| 48 ||

pādaśaucaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā śrotrabhālobhanaṃ tataḥ|
agnau paryukṣaṇaṃ kṛtvā darbhān āstīrya yatnataḥ|| 49 ||

sruvaṃ srucaṃ cābhiṣicya gavāṃ kṣīreṇa pārvati|
prāṅmukhastu mahādevi oṃkāram uccaret tataḥ|| 50 ||

homaṃ dattvā sruvāgreṇa paścāt kuṇḍaṃ samālabhet|
susamiddhāhutīrdattvā yāvannodayate raviḥ|| 51 ||

samīpe ca gṛhaṃ gatvā upasṛtya ca sundari|
ekāgraḥ prayato bhūtvā muhustiryaṅnirīkṣayan|| 52 ||

paryaṅkādutthito bālaḥ premaṃ dattvā pathā vrajan|
punastatraiva gacchantau dampatī tadanantaram|| 53 ||

iti śrīśivapurāṇe lakulīśamāhātmye saṃtoṣakaraṇaṃ nāmādhyāyaḥ||

īśvara uvāca |

tataḥ prabhātasamaye tathā dṛṣṭvā tu pārvati|
āhatustau viśālākṣaṃ putra śrānto 'asi ko bhavān|| 1 ||

iti vākyāvasāne tu mūrcchitaḥ patito bhuvi|
mūrcchitaṃ ca sutaṃ dṛṣṭvā vismitā ca sudarśanā|| 2 ||

diśo nirīkṣaṇaṃ kṛtvā patitā dharaṇītale|
saptamāsastu deveśi sutaḥ pañcatvam āgataḥ|| 3 ||

aṅke kṛtvā ca taṃ bālaṃ gatā sā jalasaṃnidhau|
devakhāte tato devi kṣipto 'asau vipule jale|| 4 ||

nīto 'asau kacchapairdevi yatra devo jaleśvaraḥ|
jalamadhye mahāliṅgaṃ tiṣṭhate ca varānane|| 5 ||

pretāñjaliṃ tato dattvā hā putra tvaṃ kuto gataḥ|
śṛṇu devi pravakṣyāmi kathāṃ paurāṇikīṃ śubhām|
yā na kasyacidākhyātā rahasyā muktidāyikā|| 6 ||

stambhayitvā ca taṃ dehaṃ kathaṃ saṃkramaṇaṃ yathā|
rodamānaḥ sa viprendro mūrcchito dharaṇīṃ gataḥ|| 7 ||

devahrade hyahaṃ devi avagāhya tato jalam|
krīḍamānaṃ mahādevi kumāraṃ paśyate tadā|| 8 ||

brāhmaṇāśca tataḥ sarve āścaryam idam abruvan|
karasaṃtāḍanaṃ kṛtvā ehyehi mama putraka|| 9 ||

ṛṣaya ūcuḥ |

bālasya caritaṃ dṛṣṭvā ṛṣayo vismayānvitāḥ|
brūhi tvaṃ ko bhavān kasya satyadharmaparāyaṇaḥ|| 10 ||

bāla uvāca |

kṣitijalapavanebhyastejasaścaiva deśāt
upacitanaraveśaḥ sambhavo dravyarāśiḥ|
śravaṇanayanajihvāghrāṇasaṃsparśavettā
kṣititalaparivartī ko 'apyahaṃ prāṇadharmaḥ|| 11 ||

ṛṣaya ūcuḥ |

namo bālakarūpāya avyaktāya namo namaḥ|
vyomapramāṇakāyāya kāmeśāya namo namaḥ|| 12 ||

vyomapramāṇavidyāya vidheśāya namo namaḥ|
vyomapramāṇakālāya kāleśāya namo namaḥ|| 13 ||

vyomapramāṇadharmāya dharmeśāya namo namaḥ|
vyomapramāṇaviśvāya viśveśāya namo namaḥ|| 14 ||

ekavajradvivajrāya bahuvajrāya te namaḥ|
ekakaṇṭhadvikaṇṭhāya bahukaṇṭhāya te namaḥ|| 15 ||

ekahastadvihastāya bahuhastāya te namaḥ|
ekanetradvinetrāya bahunetrāya te namaḥ|| 16 ||

namaste 'astu mahādeva namaste 'astu maheśvara|
namaste 'astu mahārudra namasta bālarūpiṇe|| 17 ||

namaste 'astu mahāsiddha devakhātasamudbhava|
namaste 'astu mahārudra namaste 'astu sadā hare|| 18 ||

avyaktāya namastubhyaṃ śāśvatāya ca te namaḥ|
evaṃ stavena deveśaṃ stauti yo lakuṭeśvaram|| 19 ||

sa muktaḥ sarvapāpebhyaḥ śivaloke mahīyate|
bhogārthī labhate bhogān yogārthī yogam āpnuyāt|| 20 ||

yaṃ yaṃ cintyate kāmaṃ taṃ taṃ prāpnoti satvaram|
śivasya padam āpnoti nityaṃ paṭhati yo naraḥ|| 21 ||

iti śrīśivapurāṇe lakulīśamāhātmye tṛtīyo 'adhyāyaḥ||

ṛṣaya ūcuḥ |

yaṃ cārucāmīkararāśigauraṃ saṃskāravidyāvratamantradhautāḥ|
samāviśanti pratigṛhya kāyaṃ lokapravīrāya namo 'astu tasmai|| 1 ||

īsvara uvāca |

śṛṇuṣvaikamanā bhūtvā kumāracaritaṃ param|
tadastutvā parityajya sa bālo viśvarūpiṇaḥ|| 2 ||

prākāśayat svarūpaṃ ca divyaṃ trailokyamohanam|
trinetraṃ ca sudīptaṃ ca muktakeśaṃ ca suvrate|| 3 ||

dhṛtayajñopavītaṃ ca mekhalābhasmasaṃyutam|
prahṛṣṭamanasaḥ sarve nityaṃ protphullalocanam|| 4 ||

ṛgyayuḥsāmasambandhairdivyābhistutisaṃyutaiḥ|
stotrairmanoramaiḥ stutvā dhāvamānaṃ punaḥ punaḥ|
harṣagadgadayā vācā sambhāvya taṃ ca bālakam|| 5 ||

kṛtāñjalipuṭāḥ sarve stutiṃ samupacakramuḥ|
saṃsārabhayasaṃtrastā jarāmṛtyubhayārditāḥ|| 6 ||

trātā tvaṃ parameśo no nānyastrātā vidhīyate|
ālopairmadhurairvākyairharṣeṇa ca varānane|| 7 ||

sādhu sādhu mahāvipra tava bālasya ye guṇāḥ|
stutvā te gālavādīnām ṛṣīṇāṃ tattvadarśinām|| 8 ||

viśvarūpa uvāca |

dhanyo 'ahaṃ sarve lokeṣu yasya tvatsadṛśaḥ sutaḥ|
havyasarvaprasādena yāsyāmaḥ paramāṃ gatim|| 9 ||

īśvara uvāca |

tasya vākyāvasāne tu tato 'ahaṃ rūpasaṃyutaḥ|
tatkṣaṇācca parityajya bālo mārgeṇa prasthitaḥ|| 10 ||

tataste pṛṣṭhataḥ sthitvā yathā suvipulena sā|
dhāvamānā mahādevi bālamāyātimohitā|| 11 ||

sa bālaḥ kṣaṇamātreṇa uddṛśyo jāyate bhuvi|
ūrvā nāmnā tu yā devī nadī nāmnā sarasvatī|| 12 ||

bhṛgukṣetropakārāya triṣu lokeṣu viśrutā|
nadītīre gato bālaḥ krīḍamānastu tiṣṭhati|| 13 ||

tataḥ paścimamārgeṇa śrīmatkāyāvarohaṇam|
viśvarūpo mahādevi dhāvamānaśca pṛṣṭhataḥ|| 14 ||

tasya mārge vartamāno bāndhavaiḥ svajanaiḥ saha|
hā putra tvaṃ kathaṃ yāsi māṃ tyaktvā vikalendriyam|| 15 ||

mahādānaṃ prayacchanti bāndhavā vikalendriyāḥ|
sarve viprā mahādevi krandamānāḥ suduḥkhitāḥ|| 16 ||

rātrau paribhramantaste araṇye nirjale vane|
āliṅganti tato vṛkṣān bāhubhyāṃ śokakarṣitās|| 17 ||

kecinmārge nirīkṣanti guhāsthānāni kecana|
itaścetaśca deveśi dhāvamānā dvijottamāḥ|| 18 ||

vane guhālatāmadhye vīkṣante te punaḥ punaḥ|
krandamānaiśca taiḥ sarvairuṣaḥkālastato 'abhavat|| 19 ||

evaṃ prabhātasamaye bhānunā darśanena ca|
āśvāsitāśca te sarve pratapantaḥ punaḥ punaḥ|| 20 ||

māṃ duḥkhabhājanaṃ tyaktvā abhāgyaṃ kṣīṇamaṇḍanam|
kva yāsi vatsa vatseti vadantaḥ pṛṣṭhagāminaḥ|| 21 ||

teṣāṃ sukaruṇāṃ vācaṃ śrutvāhaṃ karuṇāparaḥ|
samprāpto vāyuvegena paraṃ cakrapuraṃ prati|| 22 ||

brāhmaṇastu mahādevi manasā cintayan sthitaḥ|
tato 'apyagnau mahādevi dṛṣṭo devo maheśvaraḥ|| 23 ||

tataste prasthitāḥ sarve vepamānāḥ suduḥkhitāḥ|
mātā dṛṣṭvā bālamātraṃ mahāhlādinyuvāca ha|
putra putreti jalpantī susvaraṃ karuṇaṃ yathā|| 24 ||

viśvarūpa uvāca |

bhāgyahīnasya me vatsa durlabhaṃ darśanaṃ tava|
nivedaya tvam ātmānaṃ mūrcchito dharaṇīṃ gataḥ|| 25 ||

īśvara uvāca |

udvignamanaso viprā vepamānā muhurmuhuḥ|
mātā sudarśanā devi praskhalantī pade pade|| 26 ||

rudantī karuṇaṃ caiva snehādvai putravatsalā|
krandamānā mahādevi duḥkhitāsutadarśanāt|| 27 ||

hā putra putra putreti krośantī kurarī yathā|
pāṇibhyāṃ prapadaṃ gatvā ehyehi mama putraka|
hṛdayaṃ śokadāvāgni dagdhaṃ ca kuladīpaka|| 28 ||

kumāra uvāca |

mā mā spṛśanti munayo mama mātā pitā tathā|
asti kāryaṃ paraṃ kiṃcicchṛṇvantu munisattamāḥ|| 29 ||

tyaja śokaṃ viśālākṣi na me mātā kadācana|
śṛṇvantu ṛṣayaḥ sarve itihāsaṃ purātanam|| 30 ||

ahaṃ sarvajagadvyāpī svayaṃ sākṣānmaheśvaraḥ|
ṛṣīṇāṃ varadānāya ulkagrāme mahaṛṣayaḥ|| 31 ||

prakāśāya dvijātīnāṃ dharmasaṃsthāpanāya ca|
avatīrṇaḥ svayaṃ devi taṃ veda māṃ purātanam|| 32 ||

ṛṣaya ūcuḥ |

tvaṃ devaḥ sarvadevānāṃ kartā hartā jagatpatiḥ|
bhuktimuktipradātā tvaṃ bhogamokṣam abhīpsitam|| 33 ||

kiṃ puṇyaṃ ke guṇāstasya yena devi praśaṃsati|
ulkāgrāmasya māhātmyam aśeṣaṃ kathaya prabho|| 34 ||

īśvara uvāca |

śṛṇvantu ṛṣayaḥ sarve mama bhaktiparāyaṇāḥ|
agnihotraratā nityaṃ vedādhyayanatatparāḥ|| 35 ||

ulkāgrāmaṃ śivakṣetraṃ sapta manvantarāṇi ca|
kāmikaṃ taṃ vijānīyurnātra kāryā vicāraṇā|| 36 ||

snānaṃ kurvanti ye gatvā puṇye bhāgīrathījale|
ulkāgrāme tu tat puṇyaṃ sthāvarālokanena tu|| 37 ||

tasmiṃstīrthe madīye tu sukṛtaṃ yena yat kṛtam|
tasya varṣasahasraṃ tu pratijanma tadakṣayam|| 38 ||

parityajati yaḥ prāṇānulkāgrāme mahāmatiḥ|
divyaṃ varṣasahasraṃ tu sa rudrasye pade bhavet|| 39 ||

anaśanena yaḥ kaścit prāṇatyāgaṃ karoti cet|
anivartikā gatistasya rudraloke mahīyate|| 40 ||

brāhmāṇān bhojayet tatra tāpasān vā yatīṃstathā|
sarvaṃ koṭiguṇaṃ tasya iti svāyaṃbhuvo 'abravīt|| 41 ||

devakhāte ca yaḥ snātvā piṇḍān dadyādyathāvidhi|
ahorātroṣito bhūtvā pitR̥ṇāṃ dattam akṣayam|| 42 ||

caitramāse tathāṣṭabhyām ahorātroṣito naraḥ|
devahradataṭe ramye brāhmaṇān bhojayet tataḥ|| 43 ||

suvarṇaṃ rajataṃ vastraṃ gāvo dhanyaṃ ca medinī|
piṇḍaṃ dadyādyathānyāyaṃ mantraiśca vaidikaiḥ śubhaiḥ|| 44 ||

kedāraśca prayāgaśca kurukṣetraṃ gayā tathā|
devahradasya sāṃnidhyaṃ kalāṃ nārhanti ṣodaśīm|| 45 ||

avatīrṇo hyahaṃ yatra kiṃ tatra guṇakīrtanā|
avatīrṇāḥ surāḥ sarve sacandrāḥ sadivākarās|
anye ca ṛṣayaḥ sarve saśailavanakānanāḥ|| 46 ||

gaṃgā sarasvatī tāpī yamunā caiva narmadā|
mandākinī ca sarayūstathā ca vedakā nadī|| 47 ||

devahradasya sāṃnidhye nātra kāryā vicāraṇā|
labhante paramaṃ jñānaṃ ye cānye śivayoginaḥ|| 48 ||

etad hi bālacaritaṃ tīrthaṃ cāpi suśobhanam|
kāmadaṃ sarvajantūnāṃ nātra kāryā vicāraṇā|| 49 ||

tathāpi na tyajenmātā na bhrātā na ca sodarāḥ|
aśrupūrṇaiśca nayanairdhāvamānāśca pṛṣṭhataḥ|| 50 ||

śrīviśvarūpa uvāca |

prasādastu tvayā kāryo mama mūḍhasya sarvataḥ|
tvaddarśanena pūto 'aham ihaloke paratra ca|| 51 ||

ālokasya tvaṃ māṃ vatsa patitaṃ śokasāgare|
vivarṇavadanā mātā praskhalantī pade pade|| 52 ||

trāyasva jananīṃ vatsa varṣayogena duḥkhitām|
na mātṛsadṛśaṃ tīrthaṃ trailokye sacarācare|| 53 ||

īśvara uvāca |

vāryamāṇau samīpasthau mayā mātā pitā tathā|
mohitau viṣṇumāyābhirnājānītāṃ maheśvaram|| 54 ||

tatra sthānāt samāyātaḥ śrīmatkāyāvarohaṇam|
aṣṭavarṣakalārūpī īśāno bhṛgumaṇḍale|| 55 ||

bhṛgoranugrahārthāya avatīrṇe kṛte yuge|
brahmarātryavasāne tu ādikalpe maheśvari|| 56 ||

īśānaścottareśāne bhālākṣo devatāgaṇaiḥ|
pṛṣṭhabhāge punardṛṣṭvā jananījanakādayaḥ|| 57 ||

tato mayā dhṛtaḥ koṇo bhṛkuṭīkuṭilānanam|
tato me bhṛkuṭīṃ dṛṣṭvā sa ṛṣirdīnamānasaḥ|| 58 ||

vicetanaḥ punarjātaḥ punarāśvāsito mayā|
atraiva sthīyatāṃ brahman āvayoḥ saṃgakāraṇam|| 59 ||

mayā tu daṇḍakāṣṭhena nadī nāmā tu jāhnavī|
ānītā jāhnavī puṇyā puṇyatoyāvagāhitā|| 60 ||

sarvatīrthamayī puṇyā devakhāteṣu durlabhā|
dīrghā rekhā kṛtā yasmāt teneyam dīrghikā smṛtā|| 61 ||

durlabhā sarvalokeṣu amāyātrā viśeṣitaḥ|
dvāparasya yugasyādau meghanando maheśvaras|| 62 ||

yatra siddho mahāmegho yatra siddho maheśvari|
āśrayaṃ dehi me deva dināni katicit purā|| 63 ||

yāsyāmi svagṛhasthānaṃ nātra kāryā vicāraṇā|
tato madvacanaṃ śrutvā vṛddhadevo 'abravīdidam|| 64 ||

mamaitat saṃkaṭasthānaṃ kathaṃ tarhi āvayorbhavet|
sa uvāca punardeva ātithyaṃ kriyatāṃ mama|| 65 ||

ātithye ye guṇāḥ proktāste sarve tvayi saṃsthitāḥ|
āśrayasya prasādena mahat puṇyaphalaṃ labhet|| 66 ||

gṛhasthasya paro dharmo hi āśrayaḥ pādaśaucanam|
āsanaṃ cārghyadānaṃ ca tasmāt kartavyam uttamam|
iti prabodhito devi na dadyādāśrayaṃ mama|| 67 ||

vṛddhadeva uvāca |

brahmatīrtheṣu tiṣṭhasva brahmeśvarasya saṃnidhau|
bhṛgukṣetraṃ pavitrakṛtaṃ bhaktānāṃ mokṣakāmyayā|| 68 ||

śrīmahādeva uvāca |

vṛddhasya vacanaṃ śrutvā lakulīśo varānane|
brahmeśvaraṃ samāsādya tasminneva layaṃ gataḥ|| 69 ||

sthitaḥ sa bhagavāṃstatra kāyarūpī maheśvaraḥ|
yena kāyāvatāro 'asau tenedaṃ kāyarohaṇam|| 70 ||

asidaṇḍadharo vāme dakṣiṇe bījapūrakam|
brahmaliṅge mahādevi aham api layaṃ gatiḥ|| 71 ||

kāyāvarohaṇe puṇye tīrthe tīrthavarottame|
bhṛgukṣetrapavitrārtham avatīrṇo yuge yuge|| 72 ||

ādikalpāvasāne tu brahmakalpe purātane|
brahmaṇo manasaḥ putro 'atrināmā ca viśrutaḥ|| 73 ||

atristu janāyāmāsa ātreyaṃ nāma nāmataḥ|
ātreyādagniśarmo 'api agniśarmasutaḥ śuciḥ|| 74 ||

somaśarmeti vikhyāto dharmaśīlo jitendriyaḥ|
somaśarmasuto jāto viśvarūpo dvijottamaḥ|| 75 ||

viśvarūpādahaṃ jāto bālarūpadharo haraḥ|
yena vyāptaṃ jagat sarvaṃ trailokyaṃ sacarācaram|| 76 ||

jagatprāṇasvarūpo 'ahaṃ jantūnāṃ jīvalakṣaṇam|
yogināṃ paramaṃ brahma brahmaṇā parikīrtitam|| 77 ||

tanmām viddhi mahādevi viśvarūpaṃ jagadgurum|
carācareṣu vikhyātaṃ dehināṃ deham āśritam|| 78 ||

samāno nāma yo vāyurbhūtānāṃ viṣayātmavān|
tatrotpannaśca tatraiva mayā saṃkramaṇaṃ kṛtam|| 79 ||

lambakastu samānasyāvyāpakastu vyavasthitaḥ|
ātmarūpasamānasya prāṇināṃ paramaḥ śivaḥ|| 80 ||

avatīrṇastato martye kāyarūpadharo haraḥ|
kāyāvatāre lokeśo lokānāṃ hitakāmyayā|| 81 ||

īśvara uvāca |

īśānaḥ prathame jāto dvitīye tu mahābalaḥ|
tṛtīye tu yuge jāto vṛddhadevo maheśvaraḥ|| 82 ||

prāpte kaliyuge ghore dharmasaṃsthāpanāya ca|
sarvapāpaharaṃ puṇyaṃ śrīmatkāyāvarohaṇam|| 83 ||

koṭiliṅgasya saṃsthānaṃ śivakṣetreṇa nirmitam|
sarvaṃ tīrtham idaṃ devi vikhyātaṃ bhṛgumaṇḍale|| 84 ||

śrīmatkāravaṇe tīrthe mūrtimāñchaṃkaraḥ svayam|
cāturyugam idaṃ tīrthaṃ śivaśaktyā samanvitam|| 85 ||

bhṛgukṣetrapavitrārthaṃ nirmitaṃ śambhunā svayam|
kṛte icchāpurī nāma tretāyāṃ ca mayāpurī|| 86 ||

dvāpare meghavatī nāma kalau kāyāvarohaṇam|
śrīmāteti kṛte proktā tretāyāṃ bhūlambā matā|| 87 ||

ādau cānte mahādevi mūrtimanto maheśvarau|
liṅgamūrtti dvayormadhye svayaṃ sākṣādyugeśvaraḥ|| 88 ||

īśānaṃ kṛttikānāthaṃ sānandaṃ lakulīśvaram|
paśyanti ye narā nityaṃ te narā gatakalmaṣāḥ|| 89 ||

īśānaṃ pravaraṃ tīrtham īśāno yatra tiṣṭhati|
pravaraḥ sarvadevānāṃ sarvapāpopaśāntidaḥ|| 90 ||

īśānaḥ sarvatantreṣu sarvatantreṣu nāyakaḥ|
īśānaḥ sarvadevaśca tasmādīśāno vai prabhuḥ|| 91 ||

tam īśānaṃ samāsādhya vidhinā śuddhayā saha|
śivoktena ca mantreṇa pūjayitvā jagadgurum|| 92 ||

pradakṣiṇaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā pūjayitvā maheśvaram|
prāpnoti paramaṃ sthānaṃ bhuktimuktiphalapradam|| 93 ||

mahābalaṃ tatastīrthaṃ yatra taptaṃ tapaḥ purā|
ṛṣibhirdevamukhyaiśca paraṃ mokṣam abhīpsubhiḥ|| 94 ||

purā tretāyuge devi tīrthe tīrthavarottame|
sālaṃkāyapautreṇa nandinā bhāvitātmanā|| 95 ||

ārādhya tapasā tena divyam varṣasahasrakam|
dhyānayuktaḥ sadā tiṣṭhañjapannindriyanigrahaḥ|| 96 ||

ekacittaśca śāntātmā mama vākyaparāyaṇaḥ|
toṣito 'aham tadā devi varam asmai pradattavān|| 97 ||

trinetraḥ śūlapāṇiśca mama rūpasvarūpadhṛk|
saptarṣibhiśca bhānunā paramārthaviśāradaiḥ|| 98 ||

prāptā taiḥ paramā siddhirakṣayā lokadurlabhā|
anyaiśca bahubhiḥ siddhaistapasā puṣkalena ca|| 99 ||

apare tu yuge prāpte vṛddhadevo mahodayaḥ|
yatra siddho mahāmeghaḥ svayaṃ devo maheśvaraḥ|| 100 ||

asya darśanamātreṇa mucyante sarvapātakaiḥ|
kṣetrādhipaṃ tu taṃ viddhi svayaṃ tatra vyavasthitaḥ|| 101 ||

ghore kaliyuge prāpte devadevo jagadguruḥ|
lakulīśa iti khyātastriṣu lokeṣu viśrutaḥ|| 102 ||

tatrasthajīvalokānāṃ muktyarthaṃ naiva saṃśayaḥ|
jñānamūrtiḥ svayaṃ sākṣāddevadevo bhavodbhavaḥ|
ātmasthaṃ cintayā jñānaṃ vītarāgaṃ ca kevalam|| 103 ||

tat tīrthaṃ lākulaṃ jñeyaṃ śivakṣetram udāhṛtam|
sevyate daivataiḥ sarvairṛṣibhiśca tapodhanaiḥ|| 104 ||

tapasā sādhitastaistu surairbrahmādibhiḥ priye|
īpsitaṃ prāptavān kāryam asmiṃstīrthe varānane|| 105 ||

tatra snātvā ca dattvā ca pitR̥ṇāṃ tu tilodakam|
mucyate mānavaḥ pāpāt saptajanmasamudbhavāt|| 106 ||

saṃdeho naiva kartavya iti śambhuḥ svayam abravīt|
prayoge vā bhavenmokṣo mahākāle ca vā priye|| 107 ||

amarakaṇṭake tadvat tathā kāyāvarohaṇe|
mahāmādhiṃ puraskṛtya sasnau tatra dinatrayam|| 108 ||

anaghaḥ snānamātreṇa sa bhūtveha dvijottamaḥ|
asmin yoge tvaśakto 'api snāyādatra dinatrayam|| 109 ||

patitva brāhmaṇastatra brahmahā cātmahā bhavet|
mucyate sarvapāpebhyo nātra kāryā vicāraṇā|| 110 ||

āśvinasya site pakṣe caturdaśyām upoṣitaḥ|
devebhyaśca pitṛbhyaśca kṛtvā śrāddhādikāḥ kriyāḥ|| 111 ||

aśvinyāśca somayoge ye kurvanti narottamāḥ|
paṭṭabandhaṃ lākulīśaṃ svayaṃ devaiśca yat kṛtam|| 112 ||

na teṣāṃ jāyate janma saṃsāre duḥkhasaṃkaṭe|
tatra mārī na varteta na dāridryaṃ na rogiṇaḥ|| 113 ||

śrūyatām atra deveśi puṇye 'asmin bhṛgumaṇḍale|
śrīmatkārohaṇe tīrthe prathamaṃ tu kalau yuge|| 114 ||

dīrghakāyaṃ tu deveśi yajñaṃ yajñavarottame|
kṛtvā tu brāhmaṇān pūjya dinānyaṣṭādaśaiva tu|| 115 ||

tatra kārohaṇe dvāre viśve devā maharṣayaḥ|
bhojayeyurbrāhmaṇāñchaktyā yajamānaḥ pitāmaham|| 116 ||

yo veda viśvamadūpaṃ svayaṃ viṣṇuṃ maheśvaram|
brāhmaṇaḥ śraddhayā yukto brahmeśvaro hyajāyat|| 117 ||

ajaikapādā gandharvāḥ kiṃnarāśca tathaiva ca|
sarve devāśca pitaraḥ sacandrārkadivākarāḥ|| 118 ||

marīciraṅgirā atriḥ pulastyaḥ pulahastathā|
pracetāśca vasiṣṭhaśca bhṛgurnārada eva ca|| 119 ||

devalo gālavaścaiva vāmadevo mahāṛṣiḥ|
vālakhilyāśca kuśaśca tṛṇabindustathaiva ca|| 120 ||

uddālako jayacchṛṅgo māṇḍavyo vyāsanandanaḥ|
gautamo 'atha bharadvājo vātso vātsyāyanastathā|| 121 ||

anye ca bahavo devi ṛṣayaśca tapodhanāḥ|
dṛṣṭvā devaṃ virūpākṣam ānandaṃ paramaṃ yayuḥ|| 122 ||

yāni kāni ca puṇyāni tīrthāni saritastathā|
brahmādyāḥ sarvatīrtheṣu snātvā caiva mudānvitāḥ|| 123 ||

snāpayeyuḥ śivaṃ tatra puṇyaistīrthodakaiḥ priye|
prathamaṃ snāpayedbrahmā tataścaiva janārdanaḥ|| 124 ||

tatastvindro 'api deveśaścaturtho bhānureva ca|
caturbhiḥ kalaśairdivyaiḥ snāpya devaṃ jagadgurum|| 125 ||

vilepya candanairdivyaiḥ karpūrāgarudhūpakaiḥ|
puṣpairmanoharairdivyaiḥ śvetamālābhirarcitaḥ|| 126 ||

paṭṭasūtramayairvastraiḥ sūtrajairvā maheśvaram|
paridhāpya mahādevaṃ yathāśaktyā ca pūjayet|| 127 ||

yāvat tadvastratantūnāṃ saṃkhyānaṃ śivapūjane|
tāvadyugasahasrāṇi śivaloke mahīyate|| 128 ||

te pūjya vidhinā devaṃ surā brahmādayaḥ priye|
hiraṇmayaṃ tataḥ paṭṭaṃ cakrurdevasya mūrdhani|| 129 ||

paṭṭabandhaṃ tu ye kuryurevaṃ devasya mūrdhani|
na teṣāṃ punarāvṛttiḥ saṃsāre jāyate priye|| 130 ||

śrīdevyuvāca |

kiṃ puṇyaṃ ke guṇāstasya kim arthaṃ kīrtitaṃ vibho|
paṭṭabandhasya māhātmyaṃ śrotum icchāmi śaṃkara|| 131 ||

sāgarasye taṭe ramye prabhāso nāma sundari|
sarvaṃ tīrthaṃ prabhāsādi nātra kāryā vicāraṇā|| 132 ||

tatra someśvaro devaḥ somena sthāpitaḥ purā|
tasya dvādaśamātrākṣiḥ samānaṃ paṭṭabandhanam|| 133 ||

sakalaiścaiva yogaiśca prabhāse yat prakīrtitam|
tat phalaṃ samavāpnoti paṭṭabandhaṃ karoti yaḥ|| 134 ||

kārttike kṛttikāyoge kārttikyāṃ ṣaṇmukhasya|
darśanāt saptayātrāyāṃ tat phalaṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ|| 135 ||

ayane 'amaracaṇḍīśe yātrāyāṃ pañcabhiḥ phalam|
tat phalaṃ kṛtamātreṇa naraḥ prāpnoti pārvati|| 136 ||

vaiśākhyāṃ mahākāle adye ekādaśīphalam|
darśanenāpi cāśvinyām iti āhuśca purāvidaḥ|| 137 ||

yat phalaṃ ca kurukṣetre rāhuṇā grasite ravau|
ājanmagāmināṃ nR̥ṇāṃ tat phalaṃ paṭṭabandhanāt|| 138 ||

somavāre tvamāvāsyāṃ bhasmagātrasya darśanāt|
yātrāṇāṃ daśake yacca tat phalaṃ paṭṭabandhanāt|| 139 ||

vārāṇasyāṃ mahādevi kālakṣepaṃ karoti yaḥ|
tat phalaṃ samavāpnoti sakṛdvai paṭṭabandhanāt|| 140 ||

gaṅgāyāṃ sādhayet puṇyaṃ caturyugena yannaraḥ|
tat puṇyaṃ jāyate tasya paṭṭabandhaṃ karoti yaḥ|| 141 ||

gaṅgāyāṃ sariti puṃsām ājanmasevanāt phalam|
nā[...]kt[...] nnaimīṣādīnāṃ tat phalaṃ paṭṭabandhanāt|| 142 ||

sarasvatyāṃ kurukṣetre kanakhale [...]gu[...]lk|
yat puṇyaṃ hemadānena tat phalaṃ paṭṭabandhanāt|| 143 ||

kedāre saptayātrāyāṃ yat phalaṃ labhate naraḥ|
tat phalaṃ samavāpnoti sakṛdvai paṭṭabandhanāt|| 144 ||

kāpilaṃ gosahasraṃ tu yo dadāti dine dine|
tat phalaṃ samavāpnoti paṭṭabandhanaṃ karoti yaḥ|| 145 ||

kṛṣṇājinasahasrāṇi tiladhenuśatāni ca|
dattvā tat phalaṃ prāpnoti paṭṭabandhe kṛte sati|| 146 ||

mataṅgajasahasraṃ tu aśvānām ayutaṃ tathā|
tat phalaṃ samavāpnoti paṭṭabandhe kṛte sati|| 147 ||

sasāgarāṃ dharāṃ dattvā pumān yat phalam aśnute|
tat phalaṃ samavāpnoti paṭṭabandhe kṛte sati|| 148 ||

kanyākoṭipradānena yat phalaṃ kavibhiḥ kṛtam|
vidhinā paṭṭabandhe tu tat phalaṃ labhate naraḥ|| 149 ||

vāpīkūpasahasrāṇi devatāyatanāni ca|
kṛtvā yat phalam āpnoti tat phalaṃ paṭṭabandhanāt|| 150 ||

gavām arthe dvijārthe ca svāmyarthe yastyajet tanum|
tat phalaṃ samavāpnoti paṭṭabandhena pārvati|| 151 ||

āpannārtiharāṇāṃ ca tīrthasevājitātmanām|
satyavratānāṃ yat puṇyaṃ tat phalaṃ paṭṭabandhanāt|| 152 ||

vanāśrameṣu vasatāṃ tāpasānāṃ ca yat phalam|
tat phalaṃ jāyate tasya paṭṭabandhaṃ karoti yaḥ|| 153 ||

yastu varṣaśataṃ pūrṇam ahorātram upāsate|
ekena paṭṭabandhena tat phalaṃ labhate naraḥ|| 154 ||

gāṅgeyaṃ nārmadaṃ cāndraṃ puṇyaṃ sārasvataṃ jalam|
karoti pārvati nityaṃ tat phalaṃ paṭṭabandhanāt|| 155 ||

yāni kāni ca tīrthāni puṇyāni āyatanāni ca|
bhūtalaṃ sarvam aṭate tat phalaṃ paṭṭabandhanāt|| 156 ||

durlabhaṃ janma viprasya durlabhaṃ ca tathā dhanam|
durlabhaḥ paṭṭabandhaśca lakulīśasya ca priye|| 157 ||

svalpena hemnā lakulīśvarasya yaḥ paṭṭabandhaṃ vidhivat karoti|
vidhūtapāpo hi vimodate sa prasādam āsādya maheśvarasya|| 158 ||

ya idaṃ lakulīśasya māhātmyaṃ śṛṇuyānnaraḥ|
tatprasādena tasyāstu gosahasrādikaṃ phalam|| 159 ||

iti prapannā lakulīśam īśaṃ ye cārucāmīkararāśigauram|
saṃskāravidyāvratamantradhautaṃ samāviśanti pratigṛhyakāyam|| 160 ||

iti śrīśivapurāṇe pārvatīmaheśvarasaṃvāde tīrtha...ṇikāyāṃ śūlapāṇijanmapaṭṭabandhādimāhātmyaṃ samāptam|

samāptaṃ kāravaṇamāhātmyam|

